</p>[<a href="http://newsroom.cisco.com/feature-content?type=webcontent&amp;articleId=1208342" rel="nofollow">source</a>]<br>[<a href="https://blogs.cisco.com/diversity/the-internet-of-things-infographic/" rel="nofollow">source</a>]
